      <abstract>
        <p>Correction of Jan 5 obituary of Vincent Sardi Jr</p>
      </abstract>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>An obituary on Friday about Vincent Sardi Jr., who owned and managed the Broadway landmark Sardi's restaurant for more than half a century, misstated the year in which he was on Okinawa as a member of the Marines helping to supervise a rest camp. It was 1945, after United States forces had taken control of the island, not 1943.</p>
      </block>
      <block class="full_text">
